## Studara monorepo — root .gitignore
## Structure: backend/ admin/ mobile/ services/fastify-api/
## Goal: never commit deps, builds, caches, env/secrets, uploads, or large media.

# ── OS / IDE ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/

# ── Dependencies ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/node_modules/

# ── Build outputs / caches ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/dist/
**/build/
**/out/
**/.next/
**/.turbo/
**/.cache/
**/coverage/
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Expo / React Native caches
**/.expo/
**/.expo-shared/
**/web-build/
**/.metro-health-check*

# Native build outputs (keep sources like mobile/android + mobile/ios tracked)
**/android/app/build/
**/android/build/
**/ios/build/
**/DerivedData/

# ── Env / secrets (NEVER COMMIT) ────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/.env*.local
!.env.example
!env.example

# Common sensitive keys/certs
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*.p8
**/*.p12
**/*.jks
**/*.keystore
**/*.mobileprovision

# ── Runtime data ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/uploads/
**/*.sqlite
**/*.sqlite3
**/*.db

# If you intentionally keep an empty uploads folder, allow a gitkeep
!**/uploads/.gitkeep

# ── Logs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pnpm-debug.log*

# ── Media / large binaries (keep out of git) ───────────────────────────────
**/*.mp4
**/*.m4a
**/*.mov
**/*.wav
**/*.zip
**/*.7z

# ── Local operational notes / deploy secrets ───────────────────────────────
# Keep this file locally; it may contain operational credentials.
mobile/AMELIORATIONS.txt
# Local deploy env with secrets (use *.example templates instead)
mobile/deploy/api.env

# ── Optional: local dev artifacts ───────────────────────────────────────────
**/*.local

